      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MILLWOOD GRACE NZ (1) finished fifth at Bathurst two runs ago before a comparable effort at her latest appearance over 1740m at Riverina Paceway, beaten 12 metres. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw and rates a primary contender if she is at her best. WOKKA ROCK (9) went back last start then worked home well from a long way out to finish just 1.3 metres from the winner in second at Dubbo over 1720m, that run following his seventh there two runs back. Has the talent to take this out. DEEPWATER CAM (7) is a great chance after a string of sound recent performances, the latest a solid third at Dubbo over 2120m. Hard to find fault. KADAR (2) is worth some thought after his last-start sixth over 1730m at Bathurst on May 27. Include from the favourable draw.",
